<subSubSection id="C368652E935A8E07F2FAFAA2FB88FA7C" pageId="3" pageNumber="487" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BCD36A5935A8E07F2FAFAA2FA97FAA4" blockId="3.[151,1436,1256,1463]" pageId="3" pageNumber="487">
The genus 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D26935A8E07F37CFAA2FE4BFA81" authorityName="Motschulsky" authorityYear="1850" box="[321,410,1328,1354]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Oedesis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="487" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B906EAB7935A8E07F37CFAA2FE4BFA81" box="[321,410,1328,1354]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="487">Oedesis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
currently includes seven species with a similar distribution pattern as that mentioned for the genus 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D26935A8E07F2DDFAC6FEA3FAA5" authorityName="Solier" authorityYear="1835" box="[224,370,1364,1390]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Odontocarus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="487" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B906EAB7935A8E07F2DDFAC6FEA3FAA5" box="[224,370,1364,1390]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="487">Odontocarus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. The genus 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D26935A8E07F3C7FAC6FD82FAA5" authorityName="Motschulsky" authorityYear="1850" box="[506,595,1364,1390]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Oedesis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="487" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B906EAB7935A8E07F3C7FAC6FD82FAA5" box="[506,595,1364,1390]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="487">Oedesis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is well differentiated from other genera of Ditomi (
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B54935A8E07F6A9FAC6FAEBFAA4" author="Antoine, M." box="[1172,1338,1364,1391]" pageId="3" pageNumber="487" pagination="315 - 465" refId="ref10238" refString="Antoine, M. (1959) Coleopteres Carabiques du Maroc. Troisieme partie. Memoires de la Societe des Sciences Naturelles et Physiques du Maroc, Nouvelle Serie, Zoologie, 6, 315 - 465." type="journal article" year="1959">Antoine, 1959</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BCD36A5935A8E07F2FAFAEBFB88FA7C" blockId="3.[151,1436,1256,1463]" pageId="3" pageNumber="487">
Two species occur in the Ibero-Maghrebian area, 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D26935A8E07F13EFAEAFC74FA59" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1831" box="[771,933,1400,1426]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Ditomus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="487" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tomentosus">
<emphasis id="B906EAB7935A8E07F13EFAEAFC74FA59" box="[771,933,1400,1426]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="487">O. tomentosus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D26935A8E07F1DCFAEAFAF2FA58" authority="(Reiche, 1860)" baseAuthorityName="Reiche" baseAuthorityYear="1860" box="[993,1315,1400,1427]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Oedesis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="487" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="villosulus">
<emphasis id="B906EAB7935A8E07F1DCFAEAFBA1FA59" box="[993,1136,1400,1426]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="487">O. villosulus</emphasis>
(Reiche, 1860)
</taxonomicName>
which are readily distinguished by body size, elytral pubescence, epipleura etc. (
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B54935A8E07F19AFA0EFB9CFA7C" author="Antoine, M." box="[935,1101,1436,1463]" pageId="3" pageNumber="487" pagination="315 - 465" refId="ref10238" refString="Antoine, M. (1959) Coleopteres Carabiques du Maroc. Troisieme partie. Memoires de la Societe des Sciences Naturelles et Physiques du Maroc, Nouvelle Serie, Zoologie, 6, 315 - 465." type="journal article" year="1959">Antoine, 1959</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
